-- Serena Williams Beats Kuznetsova to Move to French Open Semis
-- B y   D a n i e l l e   R o s s i n g h
-- 2013-06-04T14:14:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-04/serena-williams-beats-kuznetsova-to-move-to-french-open-semis.html
Women’s top seed  Serena Williams  beat
Svetlana Kuznetsova in three sets to move to the semi-finals of
the French Open.  Williams, the reigning Wimbledon and U.S. Open champion,
defeated Russia’s Kuznetsova, 6-1, 3-6, 6-3 on a windy Court
Suzanne Lenglen at Roland Garros in Paris. Both women are former
champions.  Williams plays Sara Errani of Italy, who beat Poland’s
Agnieszka Radwanska earlier today, in the last four.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Danielle Rossingh in Paris at 
 drossingh@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
